             was indicted for <rs id="t18031130-15-off95" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18031130-15-off95" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18031130-15-off95" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18031130-15-cd96" type="crimeDate">13th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18031130-15-off95 t18031130-15-cd96"></join>, a looking-glass, value 2 l. eight curtains, value 5 l. twenty blankets, value 10 l. two counterpanes, value 30 s. two vallances, value 5 s. and fifteen yards of carpet, value 20 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18031130-15-victim176" type="victimName">
                     David 
                     Watson
                  <interp inst="t18031130-15-victim176" type="surname" value="Watson"></interp>
